{"word":"ὁμηλικία","slug":"ὁμηλικία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n73464\" key=\"o(mhliki/a\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ὁμηλῐκ-ία</orth>, <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ion.\">Ion.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">-ιη,</foreign> <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, <sense id=\"n73464.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">sameness of age</tr_> (so perh. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:20:465\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">20.465</biblScope> </bibl>), used as a collective, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">those of the same age,</tr_> esp. of young persons, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὁμηλικίην ἐρατεινήν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:175\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.175</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> ; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὃν περὶ πάσης τῖεν ὁμηλικίης</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:326\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.326</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:3:364\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.364</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"Thgn. 1018\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Thgn.\">Thgn.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform